Modifications by clawd/scout (agenti-main -> agenti-lite):

1) Repository cleanup / footprint reduction
- Removed non-runtime assets and docs/marketing/CI/test scaffolding from the lite fork
  (e.g., .github, docs, tests, docker/deploy extras, images, branding files, README/meta docs).
- Kept runtime-focused structure for research operation: src, dist, config, scripts, package files, ts config.

2) Tool surface reshaping for research use
- Removed alert tools module (src/modules/alerts).
- Removed portfolio tools module (src/modules/portfolio).
- Removed server_clear_cache tool.
- Removed simulate_transaction tool registrations.
- Restored selected workflow helpers for research quality:
  prompt_list, prompt_get, prompt_generate, prompt_quick, prompt_build_custom,
  research_create_plan, research_update_section, research_add_note, research_export.

3) Server startup and tool-registry behavior fixes
- Reworked server_list_tools to derive advertised tools from actual registered handlers
  (dynamic registry-based listing instead of stale static catalog).
- Added startup-time registry validation to fail fast on catalog/handler mismatch.
- Added validation script: scripts/validate_server_list_tools.mjs.

4) Server wiring and safety-mode changes
- Updated module registration in src/evm.ts to reflect lite toolset.
- Added/kept Rook-focused startup guardrails and allowlist hooks in server bootstrap paths.

5) Resulting operational state
- Callable research tool inventory targeted to 329 tools after lite pruning + selective restores.
